casebody.data:
Gregory AZOR, Appellant/Petitioner(s)
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s) CASE NO.: 4D16-4053 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Fourth District. February 01, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

ORDERED that appellant's January 26, 2018 motion for extension of time is granted and appellant shall serve the reply brief on or before March 2, 2018. In addition, if the reply brief is served after the time provided for in this order, it may be stricken; further,

ORDERED that the opinion and mandate issued in this case are withdrawn.
